body.transcript:
Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the best bowling alley in town. My name is Alex, and I'll be assisting you today. May I have your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Jamie.

Nice to meet you, Jamie! How can I help you today?

I have a question about a recent billing statement I received.

Of course, I'd be happy to help with that. Can I have your billing account number, please? Feel free to spell it out.

Sure, it's seven six five four three two one zero.

Thank you, Jamie. Could you also provide me with the date of the billing statement you're inquiring about?

Yes, it was dated October second, two zero two three.

Perfect, let me take a moment to pull up your information... Alright, I have your statement here. It seems everything is correct, but let’s double-check if there are any discrepancies. Can you specify what part of the billing you have questions about?

I noticed a charge for lane time that I don't think I used.

I understand, Jamie. I’ll look into the specifics of that charge... After reviewing, it appears a reservation was made under your name. However, as a valued customer, we can certainly resolve this issue. Let me adjust your billing statement accordingly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that’s all. Thank you for your help.

You're welcome, Jamie! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. We appreciate your patience and understanding. Have a great day!
